      <p><strong>Deferred maintenance:</strong> Homes that need new roofs, plumbing replacement, foundation work, or major kitchen/bathroom renovations are expensive to list traditionally. Cash buyers purchase as-is, so you don't spend a dollar on repairs and don't risk a deal falling through after weeks on market.</p>
